The Apple Earpods are ok but why not have upgraded items when you are paying so much for a phone. I replace the OEM Bluetooth Earpods with a higher quality OEM-style Earpod with Lightening Connector. 
Of course nobody wants to get a new phone and not get a charger/cable with their phone, so I never sell a phone without one in the box. Most sellers will only ship a phone wrapped up in some plastic. I want you to feel like you got your money's worth and experience the feeling Apple products give you when you open the box for the first time.
